                            <comment id="60016" author="bfaccini" created="Wed, 5 Jun 2013 08:09:48 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Hello Christopher,&lt;br/&gt;
Did you read my previous update+question ??&lt;br/&gt;
Since I am not able to explain what happen with these error msgs, if a crash-dump of one occurence could be available it would greatly help.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="59818" author="bfaccini" created="Fri, 31 May 2013 22:39:54 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Humm the negative sizes in the error msgs look strange but seem not significant at all ..., was a crash-dump taken at the time of one of these LBUGs in a loop ??&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
